                p Copyright © 2016 Vivint Solar Developer, LLC. All rights reserved. Vivint Solar Developer, LLC (EIN: 8O‐O756438) is a licensed contractor in each state in which we operate. For information about our contractor licenses, please visit
                    a(href="http://www.vivintsolar.com/en/licenses") vivintsolar.com/licenses
                    |.

